node.text: Thank you @officiallymcconaughey and @nascar

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jimmie Johnson on August 08, 2021 tagging @carvanaracing. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: ‘Jimmie is the definition of a team player, a fierce competitor and truly one of the nicest people I’ve ever photographed. Today didn’t end in Victory Lane but sometimes it’s hard moments like today that show the true heart and soul of a human.’ - @paridukovic

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jimmie Johnson in Downtown Nashville with @carvanaracing.

node.text: ‘Anyone else’s heart racing?! The highs and lows of Nashville street racing are real. Jimmie is a warrior out there.’ - @paridukovic

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jimmie Johnson in Downtown Nashville with @gocarvana, and @carvanaracing. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: ‘This weekend has opened my eyes to how much of a team sport @INDYCAR is. Jimmie is giving this street course his all and his team is doing the same. The passion and drive you can feel from the @carvanaracing team has only intensified after Jimmie spun today, I know it’s going to be an incredible race’ - @paridukovic

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jimmie Johnson in Downtown Nashville. May be a black-and-white image of motorcycle.

node.text: Hi everyone, I’m @paridukovic and will be taking over Jimmie’s Instagram today. I’ve been in Nashville capturing Jimmie’s weekend and am thrilled to take you behind the scenes with us in Nashville. Jimmie has such an intensity and focus during race weekends, I know he’s ready to get back in the car today and tackle the streets of Nashville.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jimmie Johnson in Downtown Nashville. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: I’ve had a solid weekend of growth in this rocket ship. Despite my mistake in qualifying, I’m fired up for tomorrow’s race!
